casebody.data:
Russell WILLIAMSON, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Jiab SULEIMAN, D.O., and Jiab Suleiman, D.O., P.C., d/b/a Premier Orthopedics, Defendants-Appellees. SC: 155147
COA: 334456 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 3, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's November 29, 2017 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
